Class MiddleLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.MiddleLayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.LayoutManager

    public class MiddleLayout
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.LayoutManager
    The LayoutManager, that will determine, where the middle Buttons will be placed in the Left Pane.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Haeldeus
